CNCP v1 22665
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#3949: Add build feature flag to enable hydration warnings in production",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:27:35.425718+00:00",
  "text": "Add build feature flag to enable hydration warnings in production\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\r\nI'm currently debugging a hydration bug in my code that only appears in my production builds (a specific node gets duplicated whenever `NODE_ENV=production`). However since hydration warnings are disabled in production, it's very difficult/tedious to manually find and add proper breakpoints.\r\n\r\n### What does the proposed API look like?\r\nA build time variable like `__VUE_PROD_HYDRATION_WARNINGS__` that allows hydration warnings to show up in production builds would be much appreciated\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request",
    "scope: ssr"
  ],
